Rating: 3
I made this recipe using a large veal shoulder blade chop, so I cooked it longer than the recipe said. Also added a splash of balsamic vinegar. I boiled the sauce down after the meat was done and it got to just the right consistency for pouring over the meat. The family loved it and the sauce was delicious with the delicate flavor of the veal. Will definitely make this one again.

